defaultLawrencedefault Tomlinsondefault: That is correct.
defaultChair:default And the Treasury said it would be possible.
defaultLawrencedefault Tomlinsondefault: No, Treasury said it would cost far too much and I said, “How much is far too much?” and they said, “A lot”. Post that I said, “Who have you asked about splitting the bank up and the costs?” and they said, “We have asked RBS”. I just said, “
defaultTurkeys
default don’t vote for Christmas”.
