defaultLawrencedefault Tomlinsondefault: I have not been able to do the split on the 1,000. I cannot keep up. As I was at pains to point out, I work as Entrepreneur in Residence one day a week. I have had to employ an assistant myself who is going through that. As soon as we get the mailbox down, it goes up. The vast majority are around RBS and particularly GRG.
default&#xa0;
defaultQ27 default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
