defaultLawrence Tomlinsondefault: Yes, that kind of thing, but it is very difficult because as well as just getting a piece of paper, I have had to interview these businesses and at the very least phone them up and chat to them to make sure, and then there is the—
default&#xa0;
defaultQ32 default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
