defaultLawrencedefault Tomlinsondefault: I think they will be shocked by the treatment of the businesses. I think they will be shocked, as I was, by the lives that have been ruined—not just the businesses that have been ruined, people’s lives—and the complete waste of an opportunity to grow 
defaultbusinesses rather than destroy them. What I think they will also find is that the cases are all so incredibly similar that there is a pattern to it.
