defaultLawrencedefault Tomlinsondefault: As overdrafts have been withdrawn it has been the only place to go. I think I may have had a meeting with the same man and a team. He spoke a lot of sense and seemed to have a lot of cases, but I don’t believe he provided me with the cases that I asked for. I may be mistaken. 
