defaultLawrencedefault Tomlinsondefault: I think we have both ended up in exactly the same place. It is an area that I have had a number of complaints in. Yesterday I had somebody text me, a man who used to be—sorry, I can’t say who he was. He had had a big issue similar to what you are explaining, which I think was a bona fide case. 
