defaultLawrencedefault Tomlinsondefault: It is very swap-esque, isn’t it? You do not bother selling a loan, you are not bothered about the margin you make on the loan, you can make £400,000 on the commission and crack on. That is the sort of thing that was identified to me, and the collapsing of the products is where they make the fee. 
